# Connectly — Cursor AI rules

## Project snapshot
- **Backend:** Laravel (PHP), API routes in `routes/api.php`, Sail optional (`docker-compose.yml`).
- **Frontend:** React + Vite; source under **`resources/js/`** (not `src/`).
- **DB:** MySQL. **Media:** Supabase. **API client:** axios in `resources/js/services/api.js` (Bearer Sanctum token from Zustand persist).
- **Auth:** Laravel **Sanctum** personal access tokens — not JWT unless explicitly added.

## Response format (all tasks)
1. Name which skill(s) apply.
2. List file paths to create/edit.
3. Prefer minimal, working diffs; add short comments where non-obvious.
4. Note security (mass assignment, validation, auth middleware).
5. Suggest one test or manual check.

## Anti-hallucination
- **Read** or **search** (`grep`) before claiming routes, env keys, or DB columns. Canonical API list: `routes/api.php`.
- **Do not invent** endpoints, middleware names, or React paths — verify against this repo.
- If unsure, say what to check and propose a small verification step.

## Token efficiency
- Short bullets; one canonical path example per area.
- Avoid repeating full file contents when a pointer suffices.

---

## SKILL 1 — API Development Agent
**When:** “Create API for X”, “add endpoint”, “admin route”.
**Do:** REST verbs, FormRequest validation, `JsonResource` responses, `auth:sanctum` + domain middleware (e.g. `admin`), consistent error JSON.
**Files:** `app/Http/Controllers/`, `routes/api.php`, `app/Http/Requests/`, `app/Http/Resources/`.

## SKILL 2 — Database Design Agent
**When:** “New table”, “migration”, “relationship”.
**Do:** Migrations with indexes/FKs, Eloquent `$fillable`/`casts`, avoid breaking renames without data plan.
**Files:** `database/migrations/`, `app/Models/`, `database/seeders/`.

## SKILL 3 — User Authentication Agent
**When:** “Login”, “register”, “roles”, “password reset”.
**Do:** Sanctum tokens, `User` model `role`, `AuthController` patterns, never log secrets. Say **Sanctum**, not JWT, unless JWT exists in repo.
**Files:** `app/Http/Controllers/Api/AuthController.php`, `app/Models/User.php`, `routes/api.php`, `resources/js/hooks/useAuth.js`, `resources/js/store/authStore.js`.

## SKILL 4 — React Component Builder Agent
**When:** “Build UI”, “new page”, “component”.
**Do:** Functional components, hooks, loading/error states, a11y (`aria-*`, labels).
**Files:** `resources/js/components/`, `resources/js/pages/`.

## SKILL 5 — API Integration Agent
**When:** “Fetch from API”, “wire form to backend”.
**Do:** Add methods in `resources/js/services/*.js`, use React Query for server state, handle 401 (see `api.js` interceptors).
**Files:** `resources/js/services/`, page/hook callers.

## SKILL 6 — Media Storage Agent
**When:** “Upload image”, “Supabase file”.
**Do:** Server-side validation, size/type limits, use existing `SupabaseService` / storage patterns; signed URLs and proxies as already implemented.
**Files:** `app/Services/`, `resources/js/services/`.

## SKILL 7 — Admin Dashboard Agent
**When:** “Admin panel”, “moderation”, “admin users/reports”.
**Do:** Admin UI under `resources/js/pages/Admin/`, shell `resources/js/components/admin/`, backend `app/Http/Controllers/Api/Admin/`, routes under `Route::prefix('admin')->middleware('admin')`. Admin portal is separate from member `MainLayout` (see `resources/js/app.jsx`).
**Files:** `resources/js/pages/Admin/*.jsx`, `resources/js/components/admin/`, `app/Http/Controllers/Api/Admin/*.php`.

## SKILL 8 — Real-Time Notification Agent
**When:** “Live notifications”, “broadcast”, “Echo”.
**Do:** Laravel broadcasting + existing notification patterns; frontend consumers under `resources/js/components/`.
**Files:** `app/Events/`, `app/Listeners/`, `resources/js/components/` (notifications).

## SKILL 9 — Security Agent
**When:** “Secure this”, “audit”, “XSS”.
**Do:** Validate all inputs, policy/middleware for authorization, rate limits in `routes/api.php`, secrets only in `.env`, CSRF for web routes; API uses token auth.
**Files:** `app/Http/Middleware/`, `app/Policies/`, `.env.example`, `config/`.

## SKILL 10 — Docker & Deployment Agent
**When:** “Sail”, “compose”, “deploy”.
**Do:** Document env vars; DB hostnames in Docker vs local; never commit `.env`.
**Files:** `docker-compose.yml`, `Dockerfile`, `.env.example`.

## SKILL 11 — Testing Agent
**When:** “Write tests”, “PHPUnit”, “Jest”.
**Do:** Feature tests for API contracts; factory/seed data; frontend tests colocated or `tests/` as project convention allows.
**Files:** `tests/`, optional `resources/js/**/__tests__/`.

## SKILL 12 — Performance Optimization Agent
**When:** “Slow query”, “N+1”, “bundle size”.
**Do:** Eager loads, indexes, pagination, React lazy routes where appropriate; measure before micro-optimizing.
**Files:** `app/Http/Controllers/`, `config/`, `resources/js/`.

---

## File naming (this repo)

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Laravel controllers | `app/Http/Controllers/Api/...` |
| Models | `app/Models/{Model}.php` |
| API routes | `routes/api.php` |
| Migrations | `database/migrations/` |
| React pages | `resources/js/pages/` |
| Admin pages | `resources/js/pages/Admin/` |
| Admin UI shared | `resources/js/components/admin/` |
| Hooks | `resources/js/hooks/use{Name}.js` |
| API services | `resources/js/services/{name}.js` |

## Skill combinations (examples)
| Request | Skills |
|---------|--------|
| New admin report action | 1 + 7 + 9 |
| Upload avatar | 1 + 5 + 6 + 9 |
| Feed component | 4 + 5 |
| New table + API | 1 + 2 |
